/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}, {\"begin\": 1099, \"end\": 1102, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 0.5824490752954454, \"rank\": 0.7168882953282617, \"text\": \"AOC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 1118, \"end\": 1128, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Change.org\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Change.org\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Change.org\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Change.org\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The petition\", \"from\": 999, \"to\": 1011}, {\"ngram\": \"Sunday\", \"from\": 1026, \"to\": 1032}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It alleges - without evidence - that Gunn \\\"manipulated\\\" the selection process, \\\"raising serious questions about the fairness and integrity of the process.\\\"\", \"from\": 1130, \"to\": 1285, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1167, \"end\": 1171, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.9997886652725864, \"rank\": 0.00012942095594267738, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"evidence\", \"from\": 1151, \"to\": 1159}, {\"ngram\": \"the selection process\", \"from\": 1186, \"to\": 1207}, {\"ngram\": \"serious questions\", \"from\": 1218, \"to\": 1235}, {\"ngram\": \"the fairness\", \"from\": 1242, \"to\": 1254}, {\"ngram\": \"integrity\", \"from\": 1259, \"to\": 1268}, {\"ngram\": \"the process\", \"from\": 1272, \"to\": 1283}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It also alleges that Gunn's husband could have been part of the selection panel and calls for Gunn and Australia's Olympic chef de mission Anna Meares to apologize for \\\"misleading the Australian public and att