etition has stirred up public hatred without any factual basis.\", \"from\": 2431, \"to\": 2500, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The petition\", \"from\": 2432, \"to\": 2444}, {\"ngram\": \"public hatred\", \"from\": 2460, \"to\": 2473}, {\"ngram\": \"any factual basis\", \"from\": 2482, \"to\": 2499}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's appalling.\", \"from\": 2501, \"to\": 2516, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"No athlete who has represented their country at the Olympic Games should be treated in this way and we are supporting Dr Gunn and Anna Meares at this time.\\\"\", \"from\": 2517, \"to\": 2673, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2638, \"end\": 2642, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.9997886652725864, \"rank\": 0.00012942095594267738, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}, {\"begin\": 2647, \"end\": 2658, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_Meares\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Anna Meares\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_Meares\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_Meares\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"No athlete\", \"from\": 2517, \"to\": 2527}, {\"ngram\": \"their country\", \"from\": 2548, \"to\": 2561}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 2565, \"to\": 2582}, {\"ngram\": \"this way\", \"from\": 2604, \"to\": 2612}, {\"ngram\": \"this time\", \"from\": 2662, \"to\": 2671}]}, {\"sentence\": \"CNN has contacted Change.org for further comment.\", \"from\": 2675, \"to\": 2724, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2675, \"end\": 2678, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNN\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.1465132212757813e-16, \"text\": \"CNN\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNN\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/r